Ishq bavla lyrics

Johd ke kinaare baithi
Soche jaun beberi me

Fikraan ne kardi saavri

Bavdi, bavdi kar di re

Re-Sa Sa-re Sa-Sa Sa-ni (x3)

Maa-gaa Ma Re-Re Sa

Be-Aayi maut na mariyo
Sootya ke teer tootenge
Mirze Jyu pyaar na kariyo
Pyaa-aaa-aar; 
na kariyo o o na kariyo

Kisse da saath diya
Kisse ta karya kinara
Kisse se milu roj
Ghar na jaun dubara

Bade roye aa Merre 
gale lag-lag ke
Padya na pith mere
Khanjar he marya

I feel alone
Tere Bina Mera Jeena Jaise
Sailaab Ke Baad
Bachi Ganga Ke Kinaare Thodi 
Rakh Ke Baad
Aankh khuli jai sunhre kisi
Khwaab k baad

Baap ke baad

Loga ne me baat liya
Tere jane ke baad
Dekh dukhaa ne chaat liya
Ee meri manjil nhi
Umar-bhar ka hoon musafir
Pyaar te aitbaar utha 
Ishq karu banu kafir

Teri tasvir me te
Ruhh bhi udd liya 
Jisam ki janjeer me te

Tere us fakir ne re
Wo to kave tha ki tu
Jani taqdeer me te(x3)

Be-Aayi maut na mariyo
Sootya ke teer tootenge
Mirze Jyu pyaar na kariyo
Pyaa-aaa-aar; 
na kariyo o o na kariyo

Ek ghar banaya hai manne
Kuch kamre usme sone ne
Ek kamra hai mehmana ka
Ek kamra rakhya hai rone ne

Re taabadtod pade aasu
Tehzaab ki tariya farsh jadiya
Koi maali bhi ni milnna re
Jab husan ka yo gulaab tadiya

Meri bebasi aalam yo
Ke puche bata ni sakda mai
Mere phone me tera number hai
Par chah k mila ni sakda mai

Ye ishhqq a, bedaarrd badaa

Dulhan ke darpan me, 
Choodi ki khan-khan me
Meera ke payal me,
Ghoonghru ki chhan-chhan me
Dariya me, naavaa me,
Shehar me, gaava me, 
Mehki fijava me
Shard havava me
Tapti hui dhoop me,
Chhayi ghataava me
Aashiq ki yaad me 
Feli hui bahva me

Ranjhe ki vanjhli me 
Heer ki choodi me
Sohni ke ghade
Mahiwal ki doori me
Tute hue teer 
patt ke maas me

Sahiba mirze ne 
aakhri saans me 
ke kahyaa hoga

Mirze Jyu pyaar na kariyo

na kariyo o o na kariyo

Logoo ree aee aee
Pyaaa aaa aa aa aar 
na kariyoo o o

Ghunt sabar ka bhar ke dekh liya
